### ============ AUTHENTICATION ============

### Register User
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "display_name": "John Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "confirm_password": "123456"
}

### Login (copy access_token from response and paste above)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{host}}/auth/refresh

### Logout
POST {{host}}/auth/logout

### ============ POSTS ============

### Get Single Post
GET {{host}}/post/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Feed Posts
GET {{host}}/feed
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Trending Posts (default: today)
GET {{host}}/trending?timeframe=today
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Trending Posts (week)
GET {{host}}/trending?timeframe=week
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Trending Posts (month)
GET {{host}}/trending?timeframe=month
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Upload Meme
POST {{host}}/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="meme_image"; filename="meme.jpeg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./meme.jpeg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="caption"

Check out this meme!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

funny
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="visibility"

public
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

funny
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

meme
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Delete Post
DELETE {{host}}/delete_post/2
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ============ LIKES ============

### Like Post
POST {{host}}/posts/2/like
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Unlike Post
POST {{host}}/posts/2/unlike
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Like Status
GET {{host}}/posts/2/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Users Who Liked Post
GET {{host}}/posts/2/likes

### ============ COMMENTS ============

### Add Comment to Post
POST {{host}}/posts/2/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "This is a comment on the post!"
}

### Get Comments from Post
GET {{host}}/posts/2/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Comment
PATCH {{host}}/posts/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "This is my updated comment!"
}

### Delete Comment
DELETE {{host}}/posts/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ============ PROFILE ============

### Get User Profile
GET {{host}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update User Profile
PATCH {{host}}/profile/update
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "display_name": "John Doe Updated",
    "bio": "This is my new bio!"
}

### ============ TEST AFTER LOGOUT ============

### Try protected route after logout (should return 401)
GET {{host}}/feed
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ============ PASSWORD RESET ============

### Forgot Password (valid email)
POST {{host}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "john@example.com"
}

### Forgot Password (email not in DB — should still return 200)
POST {{host}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "notreal@example.com"
}

### Forgot Password (missing email — should return 400)
POST {{host}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reset Password (paste token from email link here)
@reset_token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

POST {{host}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{reset_token}}",
    "new_password": "newpassword123"
}

### Reset Password (same token again — should return 400, token already used)
POST {{host}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{reset_token}}",
    "new_password": "newpassword123"
}

### Reset Password (missing fields — should return 400)
POST {{host}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Reset Password (password too short — should return 400)
POST {{host}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{reset_token}}",
    "new_password": "abc"
}

### Login with new password (should succeed)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "newpassword123"
}

### Login with old password (should return 401)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "123456"
}